&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div></description></item><item><title>中国移动宽带-解限速脚本</title><link>/p/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%A7%BB%E5%8A%A8%E5%AE%BD%E5%B8%A6-%E8%A7%A3%E9%99%90%E9%80%9F%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC/</link><pubDate>Sat, 16 Dec 2023 15:17:51 +0800</pubDate><guid>/p/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%A7%BB%E5%8A%A8%E5%AE%BD%E5%B8%A6-%E8%A7%A3%E9%99%90%E9%80%9F%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC/</guid><description>&lt;img src="/internet-speed-featured-image.jpg" alt="Featured image of post 中国移动宽带-解限速脚本" />&lt;p>这个脚本可以模拟测速过程，挂在服务器上每小时执行，就可以解除移动定期降速了。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>模拟使用speedtest测速来让移动解除限速&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="cp">#!/bin/bash
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="cp">&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1"># 定义文件下载链接&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nv">download_link&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;https://speedtest2.niutk.com.prod.hosts.ooklaserver.net:8080/download?size=25000000&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1"># 定义保存文件的路径&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nv">save_path&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;/dev/null&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1"># 使用curl命令下载文件&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">curl -o &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nv">$save_path&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nv">$download_link&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">crontab -e
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1"># 每小时执行一次&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="m">0&lt;/span> * * * * &lt;span class="nb">cd&lt;/span> /media/kasusa/hd4 &lt;span class="o">&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;/span> ./cleanDS.sh
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div></description></item></channel></rss>